1
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,879
=Ancient Love Poetry=

2
00:01:30,877 --> 00:01:33,000
=Episod 37=

3
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:34,820
Sepanjang 60 ribu tahun ini,

4
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,120
Alam Dewa timbul.

5
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,440
Dewa Sejati hilang di dunia ini.

6
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,000
Peperangan tak pernah berhenti
di Alam Manusia.

7
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,240
Malapetaka muncul secara berturutan.

8
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,040
Saya tak sampai hati
lihat manusia menderita,

9
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,280
jadi, berkomplot dengan
Permaisuri Syurga.

10
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:51,760
Namun, dipergunakan sebaliknya
kerana cuai.

11
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,640
Sekarang, saya akan mati,

12
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,600
memang padan muka saya.

13
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,200
Namun, selepas saya mati,

14
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,960
tiada orang dapat menahan kuasa jahat.

15
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:07,440
Alam Manusia mesti terjerumus
ke dalam kesengsaraan.

16
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:11,760
Saya betul-betul hampakan
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue.

17
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,360
Betara Bi Xi, jangan risau.

18
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,720
Dalam masa seratus tahun,

19
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,640
saya mesti hapuskan kuasa jahat

20
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,920
dan pertahankan Alam Manusia.

21
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,400
Selepas seratus tahun,
pulangkan Menara Tahan Roh

22
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,560
untuk menekan kuasa jahat
yang dimeterai.

23
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:31,360
Dewi Hou Chi orang yang berhati mulia,

24
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,960
pasti dapat lindungi tiga alam
pada masa depan.

25
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,920
Awak menekan kuasa jahat,

26
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,680
lindungi Alam Manusia
selama 60 ribu tahun.

27
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,480
Jasa awak

28
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,840
tak kalah kepada dewa-dewa
dari Alam Dewa yang dulu.

29
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,560
Dewi Hou Chi,

30
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,800
tak perlu menuntut keadilan untuk saya.

31
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,720
Putera long tetap anak Raja Syurga.

32
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,360
Dengan dapat pengampunan awak,

33
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:59,480
saya dah dapat bersemadi dengan aman.

34
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,360
Kita

35
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,800
tetap datang lewat.

36
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,400
Hou Chi,

37
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,280
jangan terlalu salahkan sendiri.

38
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,760
Jing Jian.

39
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,600
Feng Ran.

40
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,160
Kenapa dengan awak?

41
00:03:42,431 --> 00:03:44,480
(Ketuahan Yang Penuh)

42
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,400
Saya...

43
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,560
Abang saya melakukan kesalahan besar,

44
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,000
tapi saya tak sampai hati
dedahkannya kepada Dewa Bapa

45
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,600
kerana persaudaraan antara kami.

46
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,600
Ini bukan salah awak.

47
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,760
Awak tak perlu salahkan sendiri.

48
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,960
Saya pewaris Istana Syurga,

49
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,080
dilahirkan untuk

50
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,520
lindungi makhluk dunia dan tiga alam.

51
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,400
Namun, kalau saya lindungi
makhluk dunia,

52
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,240
saya akan kehilangan ahli keluarga.

53
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,200
Kalau lindungi ahli keluarga saya,

54
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,720
bagaimana saya dapat
berdepan dengan makhluk dunia?

55
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,720
Biarpun makhluk dunia salahkan awak,

56
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,680
awak masih ada saya. Saya...

57
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,840
Bukan saja makhluk dunia,
begitu juga dengan awak.

58
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:34,160
Abang saya yang menyebabkan
kematian ayah angkat awak.

59
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,160
Saya pula...

60
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,800
Pendek kata,

61
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,200
saya terlalu lemah.

62
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,440
Saya tak secocok dengan awak.

63
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,280
Jangan cakap lagi.

64
00:04:51,280 --> 00:04:52,840
Ini jawapan awak?

65
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,640
Seriuskah?

66
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,560
Ya.

67
00:05:11,799 --> 00:05:16,440
♪Betapa banyak kenangan
yang mengandungi awak♪

68
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,240
Baik.

69
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,360
Jangan kita berjumpa lagi.

70
00:05:20,377 --> 00:05:23,085
♪Jadi urat dan diukir pada tapak tangan♪

71
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,920
Apabila kita bertemu semula,

72
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,560
kita hanya kawan.

73
00:05:30,687 --> 00:05:35,315
♪Biarkan rinduan memeluk bayang-bayang♪

74
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,440
(Ini benda sihir Dewa Bapa saya.)

75
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,040
Sejurus ikatnya,

76
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,600
kita akan cintai
satu sama lain selama-lamanya.

77
00:05:40,615 --> 00:05:43,005
♪Cinta yang takkan berubah♪

78
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,720
Tengok, kalau awak senyum sebegini,

79
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,080
muka awak takkan nampak masam,

80
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,600
sangat kacak.

81
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,000
Awak harus selalu senyum.

82
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,520
Awak lelaki sejati.

83
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,640
Sama ada suka

84
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,000
atau tak suka,

85
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,400
tak bolehkah awak berterus terang?

86
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,880
Saya sukai awak.

87
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,280
Kalau awak sudi bersama saya,

88
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,880
tak kira apa kesusahan
yang akan hadapi kelak,

89
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,880
saya akan berdepan dengan awak
tak kira hidup atau mati.

90
00:06:08,166 --> 00:06:13,080
♪Menunggu titisan air masa
jadi senyuman♪

91
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:16,800
♪Perlukan tuah♪

92
00:06:17,182 --> 00:06:20,245
♪Barulah dibenarkan♪

93
00:06:20,815 --> 00:06:23,094
♪Dikurung dalam hati awak♪

94
00:06:23,175 --> 00:06:26,255
♪Buat selama-lamanya♪

95
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:31,480
(Tokong Jodoh)

96
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:32,720
Raja Syurga,

97
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:36,440
Bai Shuo minta semua dewa
dan betara di sini,

98
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:39,200
tolong berkati kakak dewi

99
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:41,800
dan Abang Qing Mu cintai satu sama lain

100
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,960
dan hidup bersama sehingga tua.

101
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:46,720
Cintai satu sama lain
dan hidup bersama sehingga tua.

102
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:50,800
Dapat banyak anak
dan segala-gala sempurna.

103
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,840
Betara Bi Xi lindungi Alam Manusia
selama 60 ribu tahun.

104
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,600
Jasanya besar,

105
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,680
tapi manusia tak tahu kewujudannya.

106
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,640
Bagaimana saya berkelayakan

107
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,720
untuk terima doa daripada rakyat?

108
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,440
Hou Chi,

109
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:06,640
kalau awak ingin

110
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,280
dedahkan jenayah Jing Yang
kepada Istana Syurga,

111
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,360
saya akan temani awak.

112
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,000
Biarpun beritahu Raja Syurga,

113
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,080
habis?

114
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,440
Dia takkan bunuh anak kandung sendiri

115
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:17,000
demi Betara Bi Xi.

116
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,640
Kini, barulah saya faham,

117
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,760
dalam tiga alam,

118
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:21,720
memiliki kuasa sendiri

119
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,520
barulah dapat memiliki
kuasa yang tertinggi.

120
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,080
Kalau saya bertindak
mengikut kehendak sendiri,

121
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,240
saya hanya akan timbulkan masalah untuk
Istana Qing Chi dan Dewa Bapa.

122
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:28,800
Kita perlu

123
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:29,560
cari cara penyelesaian

124
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,000
yang baik dalam perkara ini.

125
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,600
Betara Bi Xi

126
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,160
mengamanahkan keselamatan seratus tahun

127
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,200
Alam Manusia kepada awak.

128
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,560
Saya tak boleh tengok awak
menguduskan kuasa jahat

129
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,840
dengan tahap kuasa di Bukit Shen Yin

130
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,720
dan bersusah-susah berseorangan.

131
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,640
Jangan risau.

132
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,480
Saya akan cari kuasa jahat di tiga alam

133
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,720
untuk hapuskan mereka

134
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,120
agar dapat kurangkan malapetaka
untuk Alam Manusia.

135
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,880
Terima kasih, Qing Mu.

136
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:52,560
Hou Chi,

137
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,280
kalau tiga alam tempat
yang awak prihatinkan,

138
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,760
saya akan pertahankan ketenteraman
Alam Manusia untuk awak selama-lamanya.

139
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,520
Kenapa?

140
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,920
Saya macam pernah dengar percakapan ini.

141
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,160
Sudah tentu.

142
00:08:08,640 --> 00:08:09,720
Sejak kita bertembung
di Bukit Liao Wang,

143
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,760
dah banyak kali

144
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,000
saya cakap begitu.

145
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,520
Awak hanya tak simpannya dalam hati.

146
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,760
Taklah.

147
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:19,760
Kenapa?

148
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,160
Awak marahkah?

149
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,280
Saya hanya tiba-tiba teringat

150
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,760
kita berkahwin hari ini,

151
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,480
tapi tak minum arak kahwin dengan awak.

152
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,800
Tak susah itu.

153
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,080
Di sinikah?

154
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,120
Tak boleh.

155
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,160
Kalau begitu, di mana?

156
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,400
Saya dah sediakan satu tempat sulit.

157
00:08:35,299 --> 00:08:38,019
♪Bayang-bayang yang panjang♪

158
00:08:38,099 --> 00:08:41,459
♪Ia samar-samar, namun masih jelas♪

159
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:43,579
♪Hanya tinggal sedikit masa♪

160
00:08:43,659 --> 00:08:45,619
♪Untuk menyeru awak kembali♪

161
00:08:46,079 --> 00:08:51,859
♪Setiap panggilan sangat halus♪

162
00:08:52,594 --> 00:08:54,779
♪Selepas terserempak dengan awak♪

163
00:08:54,859 --> 00:08:56,979
♪Guna pelbagai cara♪

164
00:08:57,060 --> 00:08:59,859
♪Tunggu waktu subuh pada hayat depan♪

165
00:08:59,939 --> 00:09:02,019
♪Bertemu semula♪

166
00:09:02,099 --> 00:09:08,071
♪Tanpa berasa ragu-ragu
Kembara bersama awak di galaksi♪

167
00:09:08,152 --> 00:09:10,579
♪Dengarlah♪

168
00:09:10,939 --> 00:09:13,939
♪Sama-sama ada telepati♪

169
00:09:14,659 --> 00:09:17,579
♪Dekati♪

170
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,520
Sayang,

171
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,920
mulai sekarang,

172
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,520
susah senang pun, kita bersama,

173
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,640
tak berpisah selama-lamanya.

174
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,800
Ini saat penting,

175
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,840
tapi tak ada bulan

176
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,120
atau bintang pun.

177
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:32,979
♪Ikut♪

178
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:44,840
Adakah ini seperti bintang?

179
00:09:47,998 --> 00:09:50,236
♪Masa ibarat awak♪

180
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,080
Lebih cantik daripada bintang.

181
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:54,920
Betul.

182
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,560
Memang lebih cantik daripada bintang.

183
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:01,000
Awak akan pergi ke Bukit Shen Yin esok.

184
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,480
Saya rasa berat hati terhadap awak.

185
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,560
Begitu juga dengan saya.

186
00:10:08,397 --> 00:10:10,436
♪Hanya tinggal sedikit masa♪

187
00:10:10,516 --> 00:10:12,476
♪Untuk menyeru awak kembali♪

188
00:10:12,943 --> 00:10:18,723
♪Setiap panggilan sangat halus♪

189
00:10:19,451 --> 00:10:21,636
♪Selepas terserempak dengan awak♪

190
00:10:21,716 --> 00:10:23,836
♪Guna pelbagai cara♪

191
00:10:23,917 --> 00:10:26,716
♪Tunggu waktu subuh pada hayat depan♪

192
00:10:26,796 --> 00:10:28,876
♪Bertemu semula♪

193
00:10:28,956 --> 00:10:34,928
♪Tanpa berasa ragu-ragu,
kembara bersama awak di galaksi♪

194
00:10:35,009 --> 00:10:37,436
♪Dengarlah♪

195
00:10:37,796 --> 00:10:40,796
♪Sama-sama ada telepati♪

196
00:10:41,516 --> 00:10:44,436
♪Dekati♪

197
00:10:44,916 --> 00:10:48,476
♪Cakap secara ringkas♪

198
00:10:49,076 --> 00:10:52,956
♪Kalau tiada pemandangan baik begini♪

199
00:10:53,036 --> 00:10:55,796
♪Semoga awak♪

200
00:10:55,876 --> 00:10:59,836
♪Ikut♪

201
00:11:03,497 --> 00:11:05,488
♪Saya begitu pasti♪

202
00:11:05,755 --> 00:11:07,680
♪Miliki awak♪

203
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:10,278
♪Macam hidu oksigen♪

204
00:11:10,653 --> 00:11:12,640
♪Jarak yang bahagia♪

205
00:11:13,041 --> 00:11:14,799
♪Mara ke depan dengan tak tenang hati♪

206
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:18,560
♪Rasai segala-gala
yang sukar dipercayai♪

207
00:11:18,985 --> 00:11:21,412
♪Dengarlah♪

208
00:11:21,772 --> 00:11:24,772
♪Sama-sama ada telepati♪

209
00:11:25,499 --> 00:11:28,419
(Bukit Shen Yin)
♪Dekati♪

210
00:11:28,907 --> 00:11:32,255
♪Cakap secara ringkas♪

211
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:36,799
♪Kalau tiada pemandangan baik begini♪

212
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:39,640
♪Ada saya♪

213
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,560
Dulu, saya dengar bahawa

214
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:43,920
Bukit Shen Yin ialah tempat
yang memeterai

215
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:45,040
rubah sembilan ekor pada Zaman Shang Gu.

216
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,680
Tak sangka selepas 60 ribu tahun,

217
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:49,240
kuasa mantera dewa masih begitu kuat.

218
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,640
Kuasa dewa sejati

219
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,680
pastilah tak sama.

220
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,480
Namun, saya dah tanya Jing Jian.

221
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,400
Sekatan di Bukit Shen Yin

222
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,800
tak dapat ditembusi betara dan syaitan,

223
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,800
tapi alat rohani takkan dilarang.

224
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,120
Si Patung Kertas saya ialah alat rohani.

225
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,400
Biar ia ikut awak.

226
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,280
Jangan lupa selalu hantar surat
kepada saya.

227
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,560
Jika tak, saya akan risau.

228
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,000
Oh ya.

229
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,640
Sudahkah awak bawa makanan ringan

230
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,360
yang Jia Ye beri kepada awak?

231
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,400
Sudah.

232
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,240
Bawa juga ubat rohani dan azimat rohani.

233
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,680
Tahap kuasa awak bertambah kuat,

234
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,440
tapi ada banyak binatang buas
di dalam hutan.

235
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,280
Saya akan risau.

236
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,000
Sudah bawa.

237
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,080
Kuat leter.

238
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,840
Saya hanya...

239
00:12:33,432 --> 00:12:35,192
♪Di mana awak?♪

240
00:12:35,272 --> 00:12:38,632
♪Wajah yang nampak lurus♪

241
00:12:39,845 --> 00:12:41,872
♪Masa disimpan kekal♪

242
00:12:41,952 --> 00:12:44,992
♪Mengikut kenangan♪

